name: Kindleclippingextractor
body:
### Kindle Clipping Extractor
Extract notes and highlights from your Kindle clippings file and create files to import into Anki.

### Authors and Contributors
Kenrick Chien (@kchien)
tagline: Extracts notes/highlights from the Kindle clippings file and exports a file that can be imported into Anki.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
